2010-01-05    <Jim@LS-RED>

        * xspim/Imakefile, spim/Makefile Jaymie Strecker [JStrecker@wooster.edu]:
        Change install path from /usr to /usr/local.
        Removed -D option, which doesn't exists on MacOS.

