        * xspim.c, xutils.c, Makefile
        Cleanup X stuff a bit and eliminate xutils.c.

        * run.c
        Computed carry improperly in negating result after multiplication.

        * parser.y
        Bug in test in mulo (Eliot Moss).

        * inst.h
        Minor typos (from Eliot Moss).

